				<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>There's a 3 way tunnel near Droga (easy to find with a map) that has about 30-40 goblins inside that a player can easily do. Plus you can camp stuff like the Crypt Conjurer's Stone (with a little faction rebuild) or do help easily move royal raids.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I think this ring also stacks with the dain ring to get a total of a 33 ds with 8 ac in 2 buff slots.</DIV><p>Message Edited by Vjik on <span class=date_text>02-16-2005</span> <span class=time_text>05:06 PM</span>
				
